    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 V8 era. This vehicle features the sought-after 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a carbon fiber roof for optimized center of gravity. The 4.0L naturally aspirated powerplant exhibits a flawless linear power band, with throttle response sharpened by its eight individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including recent rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functioning perfectly, and the variable M differential lock ensures precise power delivery. The Alpine White paint retains its deep luster with zero signs of oxidation, complemented by a factory-fresh Fox Red Novillo leather interior. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. No accidents. Clean title. Serious inquiries only.",
